Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也把海边那次的补回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学 等下教我游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 小汐 连跳台都有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池? 明天?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:34.98,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}(18小时前)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍井同学的父母把大家的票都给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是害我改变了计划想补偿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说合宿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能来吗 其他人好像都能来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和苍井同学一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得小心不要暴露你哥哥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我别和苍井同学太亲近就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常和她保持最远距离就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共有六个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中间隔的人越多 说话的机会就越少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你会来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 我不大会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯要教我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了 手把手脚把脚胸把胸腰把腰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全身心地教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 小纯 像大叔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 村雨同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来苍井同学除了我跟别人都不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能陪着她啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小清 那边有卖咖喱热狗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:03:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 去看看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小清?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成人组
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是 儿童组
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么? 要等吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等多少年我们才能变成成人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白是明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人这样说还是会生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 今天就按这个分组活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拿来跟那种的比谁受得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋绘~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那种的」太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you Merci Danke schon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做个好梦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像突然变得有点冷清了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你冷清的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳 啊 咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会无视你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来次 再来次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真把自己当儿童了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 我要回朋绘那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该算是约会吧 是约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到夏天 泳池和泳装...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然高中生就要这样活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后手把手地教风间游泳...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 弄洒了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闹腾得太厉害了啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 裤衩的带子也松了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 要掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带子...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我重新买个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊 要哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜奶布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布丁!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西没有卖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会有吗 真会有吗 Happening
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会出现这种杀必死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了哦 我收下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...这位客人 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会在这种地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从泳池那边看到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很很很怕怕怕这这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑食可是会长不大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这个没关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停下了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后会怎样?然后会怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Fall~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 水准真高啊 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小是白的好 形状还是黑的好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像的规模要大得多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和海边比起来更是别有风情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿的时候搞得太狼狈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 只要大家都留下美好的回忆就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家各有各的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风~间~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您点的东西给您拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 莲的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯今天服务好周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 今天我什么都能做 什么都为你做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请下令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please order~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 呐 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事干吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我们去玩?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有个超有趣的节目可玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我真的很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经典情节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我们是和朋友一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?谁问你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边去 电线杆子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了让你一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边去~蠢货~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦~别再来了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经典情节...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我还有朋绘在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男孩子来和小纯搭讪也白费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?无所谓啦 我完全无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小纯人太好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的哦 不用太在意我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说搭讪的男人真的很讨人厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那干脆用我和朋绘当诱饵邀请男孩子试试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 不由地...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 有点高兴过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 最近小纯一直陪着苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是那么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久都没有像这样一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高兴了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由地...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说高兴 小莲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她高兴哦 小莲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说很好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么游呢 去哪个泳池游呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去哪玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是穿着泳装也能玩的节目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 我要回朋绘那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个龙卷风过山车貌似很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍井同学有什么想去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋绘好厉害 几乎没有水花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还有这种特长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来一次 试试那个最高的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试的话 最好别做其他动作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门外汉乱来的话 会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个呢 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳 比赛看谁游得快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然变成比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃吗? 要逃了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备 咚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由泳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛙泳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰泳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝶泳...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋绘赢了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下满意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是一次看到小纯在运动上输给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经练过游泳的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前练过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对不可能是只练过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯初中时候可是比游泳部的同学还快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都累成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然还在若无其事地游 体力有多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休学两年一定是去留学进行体育训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 要教你游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还得多休息会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是游泳俱乐部的选手吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...有恋爱过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远处传来学生们的喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好像海浪的声音一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后渐渐地消融在风里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到小汐她们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们玩得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等吃完午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我们说好的 我教你游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嘛 不过有个貌似很专业的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...是不是打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己都没有察觉到自己感情的那个境界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得才是最美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深坠爱河 无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或知难而退 如履荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地是个诗人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外两个字太失礼了 不过也称不上诗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到诗才还是你更优秀得多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的见解呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人明明互相喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不但没察觉到对方的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个甚至连自己的感情都没察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有看头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真意外地坚强啊
